Get unique 1-1 matches from mass_combine output

Source: R/mass_combine.R
get_unique_matches.Rd

Get unique 1-1 matches from mass_combine output

Usage

get_unique_matches(ms_object, pref = FALSE)

Arguments

ms_object

MergedMSObject containing match results

pref

Logical: whether to ensure every metabolite from dataset 1 gets a match (TRUE) or to optimize for overall match quality (FALSE). Default is FALSE.

Value

Data frame containing only unique 1-1 matches, where each feature appears only once
